yaws: yaws (yet another webserver)
yaws:
yaws: Yaws is a HTTP high perfomance 1.1 webserver particularly well
yaws: suited for dynamic-content web applications. Two separate modes of
yaws: operations are supported:
yaws:     Standalone mode where Yaws runs as a regular webserver daemon.
yaws:     Embedded mode where Yaws runs as an embedded webserver in
yaws:     another Erlang application.
yaws: Yaws is entirely written in Erlang, and furthermore it is a
yaws: multithreaded webserver where one Erlang lightweight process is used
yaws: to handle each client. 
yaws: 
yaws: http://yaws.hyber.org/
yaws: 

